***************
* Basic09 Linkage header

* All External BASIC09 References to this module vector
* through this routine.

ENTRYPT equ * entry point to this module
 pshs D,X save regs
 ldb [4,S] get entry offset desired
 leax <ENTRYTBL,PCR addr of entry table
 ldd B,X get offset of entry
 leax D,X address desired entry
 stx 4,S 
 puls D,X,PC vector to routine

ENTRYTBL equ *
